<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8),rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url(/assets/banner.jpg);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1><strong>EasyTravelly:</strong> Viagem sem dor de cabeça!</h1>
    <br>
    <%= link_to 'Sign up!',new_user_registration_path , class:'btn btn-flat btn-primary' %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
  <div class="card-horizontal">
    <%= image_tag "woman_in_paris.jpg" %>
    <p>Descomplique-se e se diverta no processo de montar uma viagem, organizando e juntando tudo em um local.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card-horizontal-blue justify-content-center">
  <div>
    <%= image_tag "all_in_one_place.jpg", class: "image-with-description" %>
    <p>Tudo em um único lugar</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%= image_tag "budget.jpg", class: "image-with-description" %>
    <p>Controle seu orçamento</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%= image_tag "friends_trip.jpg", class: "image-with-description" %>
    <p>Divirta-se sem preucupação</p>
  </div>
</div>

<h4 class="text-center mt-5 mb-3 titling">Destaque em:</h4>
<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide carousel-fade w-25 mx-auto carousel-home" data-bs-ride="true" data-aos="fade-left">
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="5000">
      <%= image_tag 'logo_ny_times.png', class:"d-block mx-auto carousel-item-home", alt:'logo1'  %>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="5000">
      <%= image_tag 'logo_folha.png', class:"d-block mx-auto carousel-item-home", alt:'logo2'  %>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="5000">
      <%= image_tag 'logo_correio.png', class:"d-block mx-auto carousel-item-home", alt:'logo3'  %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
  </button>
  <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
  </button>
</div>
